Astrochimp for PABST (18 x 36 in.)
Mixed media on canvas.

This was initially planned to be painted at a small event a few months ago. Due to a case of the stomach flu, I was unable to attend. Decided to do the piece anyway since we had the materials in hand.
@markdarmstrong would love to do a canvas commission. hit me up in the DMs!

Amazing work....your painted pieces are such an inspiration!
